        2262.5,
        297.4999999999999,
        2262.5
      ],
      "ignore": false,
      "order": "17",
      "anno_id": 1,
      "text": " which shows the transition probability from *i*-th state to *i'*-th one for  $i, i' \\in \\{1, \\ldots, m^{2n}\\}$ . Here, note that  $s_i^-$  shows the state  $s_i$  except for the oldest two actions. See Fig. 1-B illustrating an example of Markov transition.",
